  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 -  \u0b9c\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb9\u0bca\u0baa\u0bcd\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "IMF won't help Sri Lanka until it gets out of current crisis - John Hopkins University professor",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Deborah Prautigam, Professor of John Hebbins University, said that the country will not get help from the International Monetary Fund until Sri Lanka gets out of the current crisis.",
        "He told CNBC that Sri Lanka should recover from the current crisis and only then the International Monetary Fund will come forward to help.",
        "He said that the International Monetary Fund cannot engage in negotiations with the government when the situation continues to be chaotic, so until the government gets stability and they appoint a finance minister, there is no one to engage in negotiations with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "He said that the International Monetary Fund will not provide financial assistance if it is considered that the money will not be returned."
      ],
